=Bio=

"I am SolaRoofGuy at the www.solaroof.org wiki and I am an inventor with a life-long mission for creation of living structures and dwellings that provide for all essential life support with regenerative cycles for food/water/energy. These inventions are now called SolaRoof and are dedicated my several related Patents to a Creative Commons Public License (3.0) to provide a platform for global collaboration & cooperation that can build a world of abundance for all. I now provide most of my time/energy to the development of the POD solution for family food security and for enabling resilient communities. The POD is a co-creative project for accessible, affordable "livingry" to empower individual and collective action “to be the change” by to being a POD Pioneer and choosing to work together to birth POD Works Global as a Benefits Corporation to activate a global network of POD Preneurs. I seek 1000 Co-Missioners to join with me in this work "in service to the whole of life". Together, WE will support the launch of the POD Pioneers and the incubation of many POD Works hubs around the world. This work values and requires open hearts, synergy and a vision for living in harmony with nature, with faith that a reborn humanKind may thrive (even in our billions) with all of Life, in all of its great diversity, beauty and wildness, allowing the healing and recovery of the Earth, restoring the foundations of health and wellbeing for all."

